sition":23,"arabic":"رَّحِيمًۭا","translation":"মেহেরবান (হিসেবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_064_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":56537,"position":24,"arabic":"٦٤","translation":"(৬৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":65,"arabic":"فَلَا وَرَبِّكَ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ حَتَّىٰ يُحَكِّمُوكَ فِيمَا شَجَرَ بَيْنَهُمْ ثُمَّ لَا يَجِدُوا۟ فِىٓ أَنفُسِهِمْ حَرَجًۭا مِّمَّا قَضَيْتَ وَيُسَلِّمُوا۟ تَسْلِيمًۭا","translation":"But nay, by thy Sustainer! They do not [really] believe unless they make thee [O Prophet] a judge of all on which they disagree among themselves, and then find in their hearts no bar to an acceptance of thy decision and give themselves up [to it] in utter self-surrender.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/558.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":57190,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَا","translation":"অতএব না","audioUrl":"wbw/004_065_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57191,"position":2,"arabic":"وَرَبِّكَ","translation":"কসম তোমার রবের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_065_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57192,"position":3,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/004_065_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57193,"position":4,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"তারা মু’মিন হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_065_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57194,"position":5,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","translation":"যতক্ষণ না","audioUrl":"wbw/004_065_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57195,"position":6,"arabic":"يُحَكِّمُوكَ","translation":"তোমাকে বিচারক মানবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_065_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57196,"position":7,"arabic":"فِيمَا","translation":"সে ক্ষেত্রে (যে বিষয়ে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_065_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57197,"position":8,"arabic":"شَجَرَ","translation":"মতভেদ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_065_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57198,"position":9,"arabic":"بَيْنَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_065_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57199,"position":10,"arabic":"